    "description": "Hexaware Technologies Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Backend Developer to join our dynamic team in Gurgaon. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Hexaware Technologies Global Group:\nHexaware Technologies Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hexaware Technologies Global Group!",
